    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《逃离永明岛》是由一人工作室「蓝桃游戏」制作的叙事冒险游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>试玩版游玩时长约90-120分钟，包含了游戏的序章，以及第一个「关卡」「青华池地铁站」的大部分内容。可操作四位主角中的两位。您可以从中体验到游戏的总体故事风格与大致玩法。</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210830/extras/8eb0622c0ffda36830fb15819376a104.poster.avif?t=1752692017\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210830/extras/8eb0622c0ffda36830fb15819376a104.webm?t=1752692017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210830/extras/8eb0622c0ffda36830fb15819376a104.mp4?t=1752692017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【诡奇厚实的科幻悬疑剧情】 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>故事发生在近未来的中国，四位年龄、职业、性格、思维方式迥异的主角们前一刻还在都市中心区，现在却莫名身处无尽汪洋之中一幢陌生的荒岛别墅里。为了回归原来的生活，他们将发挥各自的专长来揭开此次「穿越事故」背后的因由。对幕后真相的了解，将会影响您的选择，使主角们步向截然不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210830/extras/1a75fa8e31fa83bf39ccc8308ef05851.poster.avif?t=1752692017\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210830/extras/1a75fa8e31fa83bf39ccc8308ef05851.webm?t=1752692017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210830/extras/1a75fa8e31fa83bf39ccc8308ef05851.mp4?t=1752692017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【丰富的人物互动和视角自由度】 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将切换操作四位主角穿梭在孤岛及各主角的「梦境主场」之中，调查、探索、与超过二十名鲜活而有趣的角色沟通、解决棘手问题。每位主角与环境和他人的互动方式、处事风格、内心思考均有其独特之处。面对困难和障碍，转换不同的角色视角或许会带来意想不到的突破。</p>",
